<p><b>What is the process portfolio process?</b> A process portfolio refers to a collection of processes within an organization that are evaluated based on different perspectives depending on the decision-makers involved.</p>
<p><b>What are the stages of a portfolio?</b> There are three major stages: planning, execution, and feedback.</p>
